thread.title: Sue L
thread.title_full: Ticketmaster Resale reviewed by Sue L

author: Sue L
title: Sue L
text: We suddenly couldn't go to a Bruce Springsteen concert, so wondered how I could sell my tickets - someone told us about Ticketmaster Resale, what an easy great service. Uploading of my pdf tickets didn't work the first time, but I received a message telling me so, think it was more operator error than the system :) Would recommend this to anyone, its still a shame though to see people putting exorbitant prices on tickets, we sold ours within days as we had a realistic price on them.
